(927, 10938, 36, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'null', NULL, NULL, 'null', '2', '3', '3', NULL, '3', 0, '2025-06-23', '7:00pm-7:45pm', 'https://meet.google.com/cqg-mzru-kiy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'completed', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'null', 'null', NULL, NULL, 'agree', 'agree', NULL, '2025-06-25', '1. Introduce Emotional Awareness Tool: The Anger Map.\r\n2. Explore the Core Belief Emerging Post-Breakup.\r\n3. Introduce the Concept of ‘The Role I Played’.\r\n4. Address the state of confusion and helplessness post breakup.\r\n\r\nGoal:\r\nDeepen insight into her patterns of emotional response, especially around the breakup and self-worth, and begin grounding her sense of identity outside the relationship.\r\n\r\nBased on a lot of improvements in client\'s state, we would officially begin with cognitive, behavioral therapy (CBT) and narrative therapy, along with components of art therapy.', 'psy_shortnote', 0, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 2, '{\"1\":{\"question\":\"How often do you feel nervous or anxious?\",\"options\":[{\"option\":\"Almost always\"}]},\"2\":{\"question\":\"What situations tend to trigger your anxiety?\",\"options\":[{\"option\":\"Personal expectations\"},{\"option\":\"Uncertain outcomes\"},{\"option\":\"Any Other \"},{\"input\":\"\"}]},\"3\":{\"question\":\"How often do feelings of restlessness affect your daily life?\",\"options\":[{\"option\":\"Severely\"}]},\"4\":{\"question\":\"How do you usually manage stress?\",\"options\":[{\"option\":\"Talking to friends\"},{\"option\":\"Other techniques\"},{\"input\":\"\"}]},\"5\":{\"question\":\"How often do you experience situations where you panic easily?\",\"options\":[{\"option\":\"Occasionally\"}]},\"6\":{\"question\":\"Are you open to exploring new methods for stress relief?\",\"options\":[{\"option\":\"Somewhat open\"}]},\"7\":{\"question\":\"How often do you feel overwhelmed or tense?\",\"options\":[{\"option\":\"Constantly\"}]},\"8\":{\"question\":\"Do you have a support network to talk about stress?\",\"options\":[{\"option\":\"Somewhat supported\"}]},\"9\":{\"question\":\"How well do you balance work and Self-care?\",\"options\":[{\"option\":\"Poorly\"}]},\"10\":{\"question\":\"How often do you engage in self-care routines?\",\"options\":[{\"option\":\"Weekly\"},{\"option\":\"Occasionally\"}]}}', NULL, 0, '2025-06-23 12:29:38', '2025-06-23 12:29:38');
