(956, 10999, 44, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'null', NULL, NULL, 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '2025-10-21', '12:00pm-12:45pm', 'https://meet.google.com/mem-hwzg-zyr', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'completed', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'null', 'null', NULL, NULL, 'null', 'null', 'CLINICAL PSYCHOLOGICAL REPORT\r\n\r\nI. Identifying Information\r\nClient Name: Shiva \r\nAge: Adult male\r\nGender: Male\r\nReferral Source: Self-referred\r\nExaminer: Anushka\r\n\r\nII. Reason for Referral\r\nThe client sought psychological consultation due to emotional distress related to family conflict, cognitive difficulties, sleep disturbance, social isolation, self-image concerns, and career uncertainty.\r\n\r\nIII. Presenting Complaints\r\n1. Distress due to frequent parental conflicts\r\n2. Difficulty concentrating and maintaining consistency\r\n3. Irregular sleep patterns\r\n4. Social isolation\r\n5. Low confidence related to self-image\r\n6. Career-related confusion\r\n\r\nIV. History of Presenting Illness\r\nThe client reported a chronically stressful home environment marked by frequent parental arguments. Over time, he noticed reduced concentration, disrupted sleep, emotional exhaustion, and increased career-related anxiety.\r\n\r\nV. Past Psychological History\r\nHistory of prior therapy for self-image and confidence issues. No psychiatric hospitalization reported.\r\n\r\nVI. Family History\r\nOngoing marital discord between parents. Brother no longer resides at home.\r\n\r\nVII. Mental Status Examination\r\nMood: Anxious and low\r\nAffect: Constricted\r\nThought Process: Logical, ruminative\r\nInsight: Fair\r\nJudgment: Intact\r\nRisk: No suicidal or homicidal ideation reported\r\n\r\nVIII. Provisional Diagnosis (DSM-5-TR)\r\nAdjustment Disorder with Mixed Anxiety and Depressed Mood (F43.23)\r\n\r\nIX. Treatment Recommendations\r\n- Individual psychotherapy\r\n- Cognitive-behavioral interventions\r\n- Sleep hygiene\r\n- Regular exercise\r\n- Career counseling\r\n- Social reconnection\r\n\r\nX. Prognosis\r\nPrognosis is fair to good with consistent therapeutic support.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', NULL, NULL, 'psy_shortnote', 0, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 3, NULL, 0, 0, '2025-10-20 20:19:18', '2025-10-20 20:19:18'),
